#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:906-5
msgid ""
"We also have different boxes throughout the guide to inform or warn you:"
msgstr ""
"Skozi celoten priročnik uporabljamo tudi različne okvirčke za obveščanje ali "
"opozarjanje:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:908-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">WARNING</span> I am a warning box. I explain "
"things when you need to be extra careful."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">OPOZORILO</span> Sem opozorilni okvirček. "
"Pojasnjujem stvari, pri katerih moraš biti posebej pazljiv."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:910-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> I am an info box. I give contextual "
"information or extra explanations."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> Sem informativni okvirček. Podajam "
"vsebinski kontekst ali dodatna pojasnila."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:912-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">TIP</span> I am a tip box. I contain tips that "
"makes your life easier when using KOReader."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_green\">NASVET</span> Sem okvirček z nasvetom. Vsebuje "
"namige, ki ti olajšajo uporabo KOReaderja."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div:914-5
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">!!! ADVANCED</span> I am an <b>ADVANCED</b> tag. "
"If you see me on a topic, it means that you need to have a certain degree of "
"technical knowledge like working with a file system, CSS knowledge, "
"installation of external files etc. depending on the procedure."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"label_red\">!!! NAPREDNO</span> Sem oznaka <b>NAPREDNO</b>. Če "
"me vidiš pri kakšni temi, to pomeni, da potrebuješ določeno stopnjo "
"tehničnega znanja, kot je delo z datotečnim sistemom, znanje CSS, nameščanje "
"zunanjih datotek itd., odvisno od postopka."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:918-2
msgid ""
"KOReader is developed and supported by volunteers all around the world. You "
"can be a part of this project too by:"
msgstr ""
"KOReader razvijajo in podpirajo prostovoljci z vsega sveta. Tudi ti si lahko "
"del tega projekta, tako da:"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:920-3
msgid "Fixing bugs and implementing new features"
msgstr "odpravljaš hrošče in uvajaš nove funkcije,"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:921-3
msgid ""
"Translating the program into your language or improving an existing "
"translation"
msgstr "prevajaš program v svoj jezik ali izboljšuješ obstoječi prevod,"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:922-3
msgid ""
"Helping others with your knowledge in the forums or on GitHub issues and "
"discussions"
msgstr "Pomagaš drugim s svojim znanjem na forumih ali v razpravah na GitHubu"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.p:925-9
msgid "Check <a href=\"#L1-reachus\">Reach us</a> section for the links."
msgstr ""
